Mg_abc_of_toilet - small funny map :)

There are many traps, watch out for a RUNNING PIGS AND TOILETS!

If you step up to the wrong toilet you will explode, trap for 30 sec and listen to "sounds of pigs".

Good toilet - weapon ( scout, grenade, knife, deagle, tmp)

THERE ARE FLYING KNIFES!

If you will pick up one of two knifes at top of map, you can FLY!
